# CSC Config Repository Git Attributes
# Ensures consistent line endings and diff behavior across platforms.

# Default: auto-detect and normalize
* text=auto

# Shell scripts: always LF
*.sh text eol=lf

# Config files: always LF (servers typically run Linux)
*.cfg text eol=lf

# Hook template: always LF
*.hook text eol=lf

# Markdown: auto (platform-native)
*.md text

# Generated file - mark for merge conflict awareness
modes.md merge=union